quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  89,24,"O wi'a haaniino mi ardinii golle lobbe wonan'de nguurndam am."
  89,25,"E oon √Īalawma hay gooto le…ďtatah hono lepte mum."
  89,26,"Hay go'oto tonngetaake hono tonngi heefer…ďe."
  89,27,"Ehey ma fittaandu hu…ďandiindu."
  89,28,"Rutto e joom ma ha…óa woni belaa…óo mbo KaŇčko ne hombo wela ma."
  89,29,"Naat e maccu…ďe am."
  89,30,"Naat e aljanna am."
  90,1,"Mbi…óa woo…óndira e ndii lesdi."
  90,2,"Aan ha…óa daganana ndii lesdi."
  90,3,"E jipnaa…óo e ko jibini."
  90,4,"Ko goongo min tagii ne…ó…óo e ndeer tampere."
  90,5,"Mbele o sikkat ala baaw…óo e makko hay hu'unde."
  90,6,"O wi'a mi tottarii jawdi keewndi."
  90,7,"Mbele o sikku hay gooto yiaani mbo."
  90,8,"Mbele min in mba…óanaani mbo gite …ói…óe."
  90,9,"E …óemngal yo toni …ói…ói."
  90,10,"Min peewni …óum laabi …ói…ói."
  90,11,"Ko ha…ói …óum falgude palal."
  90,12,"Ko hol…óum anndin maa ko woni palal?"
  90,13,"Ko rim…óin'de daande."
  90,14,"Wollo √Īammin'de e √Īalngu heege sa…ótunge."
  90,15,"Alyatiime e jiidaa…óo ko …ďadii."
  90,16,"Wollo ndeen miskiin baas…óo sanne."
  90,17,"Refti o laati ummaade e …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe mbasandiri mou√Īal …ďe mbasandiri e yurmeende."
  90,18,"Ko …ďeen ngoni joom en √Īaame."
  90,19,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe aayeeje amen ngoni yim…ďe nane."
  90,20,"Hina e dow ma…ď…ďe jayngol sokaaange."